name: SciFinder Scholar
description: Contains information on more than 40 million substances and 18 million reactions (searchable by structure, formula, and chemical identifier) as well as over 30 million references, including journal articles, patents and other documents. **Please note that all patrons must create a personal account on first use at https://origin-scifinder.cas.org/registration/index.html?corpKey=7BF1F3BB-86F3-F00A-11C8-5FB99669A39B in order to use this resource.
